<item>
            <title>[HBASE-13559] Region stuck in PENDING_OPEN on repeated master failure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-13559</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We had some regions stay un-assigned. They were in pending open on a server that was dead. The cluster was restarted as a whole a few times and then the regions were stuck until a manual assign was performed on them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I know timing things out has been a pain. Could we have a timeout on servers that are not alive?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
